    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And besides, I didn't realize that they had election a day before, the 6th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All the papers, you know the advertisements, what they threw, for the candidates was all on the floor.",
