    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I didn't see that in Austria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, so it basically, it made a very bad impression on me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But thanks, God, I'm very glad I came here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was just an impression, a bad impression.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But basically life, life wasn't-- wasn't that bad here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
